wpkg (0.9.2) stable unstable; urgency=medium

  * Fixed the advgetopt parser to properly handle single parameters so we
    really keep only the last one used.
  * Strengthen the advgetopt parser to break in more cases as it was first
    expected (especially useful for developers).
  * Fixed the strcasecmp() to properly compare UTF-8 strings.
  * Fixed the number of items check in get_string() and similar.
  * Fixed a number of 'unpack' or 'install' references in wpkgar_remove.cpp.
  * Added some logs in the remove process in case of failure.
  * Changed the calling of scripts to use deconfigure or purge as required.
  * Fixed the name of the SunOS operating system: solaris.
  * The build script now automatically creates a source package.
  * The build script copies the output to our wpkg archive.
  * Fixed the usage() function that would write some information using stderr
    and others with stdout and call fflush on stdout once done.
  * Fixed the wpkg_filename class so it compiles under FreeBSD and Solaris.
  * Added a script to run devenv.exe the 6x we need to build everything.
  * Fixed the name of the OS under Microsoft Windows.

